I'm just doing a few last things as far as updates go, and then stepping back and simply curating the github page.http://www.minecraftforum.net/forums/mapping-and-modding/minecraft-mods/1292222-ars-magica-2-version-1-4-0-009-updated-february-8?comment=9840
